title: Captain America (001 - 013) (2013) (ongoing) (- Nem -)
description: Too frail to enlist in the U.S. Military during World War II, Steve Rogers volunteered to receive the experimental Super-Soldier Serum. Enhanced to the pinnacle of human physical potential he became Captain America. Fighting the Axis powers, Steve became an American icon. Accidentally put into suspended animation near the war's end, Steve was awakened decades later and became the leader of the Avengers. Captain America is a living legend and the embodiment of freedom.
